description:
Torchlighters: The Martin Luther Story (Spanish) | Full Episode | Stephen Daltry | David Reggi

Martin Luther didnt mean to spark the Reformation with his 95 Theses, but his realization that salvation comes through faith and not works ignited the revolution that changed the world. As Pope Leo X hounds and fights him at every turn, will Luther have the courage to stand strongeven to death? Find out with the fifteenth episode of the Torchlighters, commemorating the 500th anniversary of the Reformation!

In a world ruled by the church, all it took was one little nail, one well-written scroll, and one sharp-tongued monk to turn everything upside-down! Martin Luther didnt mean to spark the Reformation with his 95 Theses, but his realization that salvation comes through faith and not works ignited the revolution that changed the world. As Pope Leo X hounds and fights him at every turn, will Luther have the courage to stand strongeven to death? Find out with the fifteenth episode of the Torchlighters, commemorating the 500th anniversary of the Reformation!

Director: Robert Fernandez
Starring: Stephen Daltry, David Reggi
